title: C08W 4G GPS Tracker
metaDesc: High-precision C08W 4G GPS tracking device offering real-time location monitoring and advanced fleet analytics.
fullDescription: The C08W is a professional-grade 4G GPS tracker designed for comprehensive fleet management. It provides precise real-time positioning, allowing fleet managers to monitor vehicle locations instantly. Equipped with anti-theft features and robust connectivity, it ensures asset safety in various environments.
features: Compact design with IP65 water resistance
packaging: 1x C08W Unit, 1x Power Cable, 1x User Manual, 1x Relay (Optional)
